# Remove .DS_Store from git if it's already tracked
git rm --cached .DS_Store

# Create the .gitignore (copy the content from the artifact)
# Then add it
git add .gitignore
```

**You should also have `.gitignore` files in subdirectories:**

**`frontend/.gitignore`:**
```
# Dependencies
node_modules/
package-lock.json

# Build output
dist/
dist-ssr/
*.local

# Vite
.vite/

# Environment
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# Editor
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea/

# OS
.DS_Store
```

**`java-service/.gitignore`:**
```
# Maven
target/
pom.xml.tag
pom.xml.releaseBackup
pom.xml.versionsBackup
dependency-reduced-pom.xml

# IDE
.idea/
*.iml
*.iws
*.ipr

# Logs
*.log

# OS
.DS_Store

# Application
application-local.yml